{"tid":927202,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【蕭生升仙】hmv 欠租 HMV數碼中國崩盤式挫8成變「升仙」","createTime":"2018-12-04T04:14:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-04T06:06:49.000Z","uid":37661,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"ae9ca5326c83db2d3b1a30c5ef412617c881a8b0","tid":927202,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T04:14:50.000Z","msg":"hmv 欠租 HMV數碼中國崩盤式挫8成變「升仙」<br />\n<br />\n連鎖唱片公司hmv再被追租485萬元，母企HMV數碼中國（08078）今日洗倉式下跌8成，最新報0.032元，淪為「仙股」。<br />\n<br />\nhmv自上月起，相繼被業主追討租金及貸款，旗下銅鑼灣百德新街分店及中環萬年大廈分店的業主今日（3日）同日入禀高等法院，向hmv追討租金及相關費用共逾485萬元，要求交還舖位。<br />\n<br />\nHMV數碼中國上季虧損近5,300萬元，當中hmv業務收入3,155萬港元，按年下跌4成，股價今日裂口大跌8成，低見0.025元，現跌79%報0.032元，成交暫錄6,900萬元。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://wealth.hket.com/article/2222601/hmv%E6%AC%A0%E7%A7%9F%20%20%20HMV%E6%95%B8%E7%A2%BC%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%B4%A9%E7%9B%A4%E5%BC%8F%E6%8C%AB8%E6%88%90%E8%AE%8A%E3%80%8C%E5%8D%87%E4%BB%99%E3%80%8D?mtc=b0002\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwealth.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2222601%2Fhmv%25E6%25AC%25A0%25E7%25A7%259F%2520%2520%2520HMV%25E6%2595%25B8%25E7%25A2%25BC%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25B4%25A9%25E7%259B%25A4%25E5%25BC%258F%25E6%258C%25AB8%25E6%2588%2590%25E8%25AE%258A%25E3%2580%258C%25E5%258D%2587%25E4%25BB%2599%25E3%2580%258D%3Fmtc%3Db0002&d=c2Oj08GKES16mIsH3YW0tkbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=906f5316\" target=\"_blank\">https://wealth.hket.com/article/2222601/hmv%E6%AC%A0%E7%A7%9F%20%20%20HMV%E6%95%B8%E7%A2%BC%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%B4%A9%E7%9B%A4%E5%BC%8F%E6%8C%AB8%E6%88%90%E8%AE%8A%E3%80%8C%E5%8D%87%E4%BB%99%E3%80%8D?mtc=b0002</a>"},{"pid":"4e2f6fa9bc8f1d99c00e9e1239eef1a7d2d50376","tid":927202,"uid":145277,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T04:16:01.000Z","msg":"燒山又有燈呢間野？"},{"pid":"1b2b2b0a1c7c5bfe3c418e423c26f4ac973d4c27","tid":927202,"uid":145277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T04:17:18.000Z","msg":"真係惹著燒山無運行"},{"pid":"57e90e66c6da9f07a6150325c2d1eaae5bf7c4